#!/usr/local/projects/routing/help/html_filter.pl
<h2 align=center>Help for "Account fullname"</h2>
To use this software, you must login to the Brightsands software suite.
In most cases, you will be given an account (and privileges) on this system by
the software administrator, but in some cases you can create the account
yourself.
<p>To create an account for yourself, in addition to other things, you must
type in your full name.
